name: decor8ai
description: Decor8 AI is an AI Interior Design Platform. With Decor8 AI Javascript SDK, you can automate various interior design generation tasks such as virtually staging an empty room or re-designing a room with its photo. You can also use Decor8 AI Javascript SDK to generate interior design ideas for a room based on your preferences.
author: Akhilesh Joshi <akhilesh@immex.tech>
